{"tid":36722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華過去一個月　約晤鄭家純、李澤楷、林建岳、馬道立、沈祖堯等人","createTime":"2016-12-13T01:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:18:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e240119002e175eed4d353e2f412c7a965dae435","tid":36722,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"曾俊華昨日請辭財政司司長，預料日內將會正式宣佈參選特首，《蘋果日報》今天頭條報道，該報最近個多月追蹤財爺，發現他頻頻拜會手握選委票、兼具影響力的政商界城中超級富豪及財團「大孖沙」，疑似提早秘密拉票，為爭奪特首寶座鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》報道，曾俊華密會的政商界名人，至少包括被視為梁粉的新世界集團主席「純官」鄭家純、長和系李嘉誠的次子李澤楷、嘉華集團主席呂志和、麗新系的林建岳、香港美國商會前主席詹康信、富豪潘迪生、前立法會議員霍震霆，以及終審法院首席法官馬道立、與中文大學校長沈祖堯等。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》的報道又指，據傳會參與助選活動的財爺兒子曾雕龍亦不時現身。"},{"pid":"4a71ec57978bf0196ff0c97199aba225fb1c1ba0","tid":36722,"uid":28892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"仲以為係雞排妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef393421dbf17086f205c8abe9028c141a98e903","tid":36722,"uid":1934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為係雞排妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a3fe3b482e4ea4e6e3a089c71a2ea1f5f28d94","tid":36722,"uid":51058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲以為係雞排妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0078cefb61cd990487407f2ce9b086544ce4b4","tid":36722,"uid":59692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲以為係雞排妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都睇